com.gemalto.idp.mobile.core.util

Class SecureList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gemalto.idp.mobile.core.util.SecureList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - List data type

    public final class SecureList<T>
extends Object
    Secure list object. This list increases the security protection of passing list data type (e.g. from being hooked) as compared to the original Java List.
    Since:
    5.4
